Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.05,0:00:12.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh my, hold on there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.47,0:00:14.60,Main,,0,0,0,,This isn't working at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.60,0:00:16.31,Main,,0,0,0,,They just keep fluttering.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.77,0:00:24.73,Main,,0,0,0,,So sparkly...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.73,0:00:26.69,Main,,0,0,0,,So pretty...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.71,0:00:45.75,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The truth rests solely on{\i0}\N{\i1}the front/back of a card{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.75,0:00:51.05,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It has not yet been solved{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.05,0:01:01.06,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Upon the dazzling, dizzying stage,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.06,0:01:12.41,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}destroy those entangled emotions{\i0}\N{\i1}as many times as it takes to satisfy you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.41,0:01:17.62,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What should the tomorrows{\i0}\N{\i1}wandering after fate's beckoning{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.62,0:01:23.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}choose and discard so that{\i0}\N{\i1}they can become one?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.00,0:01:28.46,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't afford to disclose my reproachable hand{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.46,0:01:33.55,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The days spent draining{\i0}\N{\i1}the already-dry sea of regret{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.55,0:01:38.97,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}desire within limited words forgiveness{\i0}\N{\i1}for the unplanned smile{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.97,0:01:43.85,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't mind forgetting reality{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.85,0:01:48.98,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't want to know anything now{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.98,0:01:50.23,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.24,0:01:59.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.87,0:02:05.54,Main,,0,0,0,,That scrunchie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.42,0:02:08.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.21,0:02:11.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.05,0:02:13.05,Main,,0,0,0,,regained my memory...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.05,0:02:14.76,Main,,0,0,0,,of both of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.76,0:02:16.43,Main,,0,0,0,,back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.39,0:02:19.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.43,0:02:21.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.10,0:02:23.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.73,0:02:25.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.90,0:02:27.77,Main,,0,0,0,,It hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.77,0:02:32.28,Main,,0,0,0,,It felt like my chest was being torn apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.28,0:02:36.03,Main,,0,0,0,,But, I still thought to myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.03,0:02:39.37,Main,,0,0,0,,I... want to remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.37,0:02:40.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.62,0:02:43.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if it was painful, or it hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.58,0:02:45.50,Main,,0,0,0,,I still wanted...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.50,0:02:47.38,Main,,0,0,0,,...to remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.38,0:02:48.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.92,0:02:53.05,Main,,0,0,0,,W-Well then, why'd you\Nhide that from us until now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.05,0:02:55.68,Main,,0,0,0,,I wanted my wish to come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.68,0:02:57.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I wanted friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.89,0:03:01.72,Main,,0,0,0,,No... What I wished for didn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.72,0:03:06.81,Main,,0,0,0,,As long as I won, Yuzuki\Nwould become an Eternal Girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.81,0:03:08.94,Main,,0,0,0,,and be released from the card.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.27,0:03:11.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.86,0:03:16.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you saying, Hitoe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.57,0:03:18.87,Main,,0,0,0,,That wouldn't solve anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.87,0:03:21.74,Main,,0,0,0,,You would be in my...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.74,0:03:26.25,Main,,0,0,0,,My friends are thinking this much of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.25,0:03:30.75,Main,,0,0,0,,To me, that's almost like a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.75,0:03:34.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Someone sacrificing their own life for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.88,0:03:37.09,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't know
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.09,0:03:40.43,Main,,0,0,0,,such a beautiful thought\Never existed in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.76,0:03:44.89,Main,,0,0,0,,More than having a world of Selectors...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.89,0:03:46.69,Main,,0,0,0,,to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.69,0:03:49.23,Main,,0,0,0,,meeting the both of you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.23,0:03:50.85,Main,,0,0,0,,is way...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.85,0:03:52.82,Main,,0,0,0,,way more...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.82,0:03:55.07,Main,,0,0,0,,of a miracle to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.74,0:04:03.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Being able to do something for a friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.24,0:04:06.79,Main,,0,0,0,,There's nothing more beautiful than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.79,0:04:11.50,Main,,0,0,0,,To me, there's no other wish\NI want granted besides that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.50,0:04:13.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.59,0:04:20.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.93,0:04:24.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Please, Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.35,0:04:27.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Please listen to my wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.02,0:04:28.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.31,0:04:30.85,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to release her from the card.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.85,0:04:33.40,Main,,0,0,0,,My friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.40,0:04:35.44,Main,,0,0,0,,My precious friend...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.87,0:04:46.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Then can Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.45,0:04:49.41,Main,,0,0,0,,become friends with Ru?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.75,0:04:53.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.67,0:04:55.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Tell Tama what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.46,0:04:56.42,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:04:58.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama needs to battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.72,0:05:02.26,Main,,0,0,0,,To make Ru's wish come true...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.26,0:05:07.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama needs to battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.26,0:05:08.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.64,0:05:11.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.94,0:05:13.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.48,0:05:14.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's continue the battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.94,0:05:18.28,Main,,0,0,0,,And... I'm sorry Hitoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.28,0:05:21.15,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm going to win this battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.15,0:05:24.12,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm going to have my wish come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.12,0:05:25.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.57,0:05:27.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Arc Aura!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.34,0:05:43.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.06,0:05:50.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.23,0:05:54.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Did that hurt, Yuzuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.65,0:05:55.90,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.90,0:05:58.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Anyways, Ruko, about that earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.23,0:06:00.94,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right! Ruko, your wish is to...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.86,0:06:07.41,Main,,0,0,0,,For Yuzuki, and all the girls\Nwho were sealed into cards,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.41,0:06:09.12,Main,,0,0,0,,to be released.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.12,0:06:09.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.91,0:06:11.50,Main,,0,0,0,,W-Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.50,0:06:14.50,Main,,0,0,0,,I told you before that\Nwe should think about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.50,0:06:19.21,Main,,0,0,0,,I feel the same way\Nas both of you, Hitoe, Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.21,0:06:23.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Being able to do something for your friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.22,0:06:25.97,Main,,0,0,0,,is something to be really happy about!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.93,0:06:33.02,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.35,0:06:37.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait! I'll go too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.52,0:06:39.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.15,0:06:42.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe... Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.28,0:06:44.61,Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.61,0:06:48.07,Main,,0,0,0,,I give up. No use trying to talk you out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.07,0:06:50.20,Main,,0,0,0,,If your wish comes true,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.20,0:06:52.91,Main,,0,0,0,,I should be back to normal
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.91,0:06:56.25,Main,,0,0,0,,and you shouldn't become an LRIG too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.25,0:06:59.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's buy dumplings at the\Nconvenience store and head home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.88,0:07:02.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.60,0:07:20.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama. Let's go shopping\Nfor other stuff besides dumplings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.36,0:07:21.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Shopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.94,0:07:26.28,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm going to buy you\Na matching pair of scruchies too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.28,0:07:27.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.42,0:07:47.80,Main,,0,0,0,,It's scary being up so high here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.80,0:07:51.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru and Grandma's house\Nis probably around there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.48,0:07:58.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Grandma...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.52,0:08:05.36,Main,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.36,0:08:06.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.78,0:08:08.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.32,0:08:10.62,Main,,0,0,0,,You folks came too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.62,0:08:12.16,Main,,0,0,0,,What's it to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.16,0:08:14.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Not like we're going to\Nget in the way or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.08,0:08:16.25,Main,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.25,0:08:19.29,Main,,0,0,0,,It won't make a difference\Nif there's an audience or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.29,0:08:21.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you need anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.33,0:08:23.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Like an expression of determination?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.75,0:08:26.09,Main,,0,0,0,,How about details of what's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.47,0:08:30.84,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't need anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.35,0:08:34.51,Main,,0,0,0,, I only want to battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.51,0:08:36.27,Main,,0,0,0,,You're the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.06,0:08:41.44,Main,,0,0,0,,--Open!\N--Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.87,0:08:56.70,Main,,0,0,0,,What a lonely place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.70,0:08:59.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Is... this the image within your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.96,0:09:03.08,Main,,0,0,0,,You said you "only want to battle," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.50,0:09:06.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.02,0:09:23.94,Main,,0,0,0,,You're first, Ru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.44,0:09:26.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Grow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.99,0:09:32.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Grow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.33,0:09:40.58,Main,,0,0,0,,They're both strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.58,0:09:42.79,Main,,0,0,0,,But, Ruko...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.79,0:09:46.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Her eyes are so cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.50,0:09:49.34,Main,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.34,0:09:52.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Unlike the battles before, it doesn't feel fun
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.84,0:09:55.60,Main,,0,0,0,,or exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.35,0:10:02.85,Main,,0,0,0,,It's so quiet...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.98,0:10:11.07,Main,,0,0,0,,I can even hear Tama breathing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.61,0:10:15.03,Main,,0,0,0,,This is the battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.03,0:10:16.66,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.41,0:10:18.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Grow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.41,0:10:22.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Sword Ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.22,0:10:38.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Urith.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.10,0:10:40.85,Main,,0,0,0,,She's in a league of her own!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.56,0:10:48.19,Main,,0,0,0,,You already had enough wins\Nto give birth to an Eternal Girl
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.19,0:10:50.90,Main,,0,0,0,,but, the time wasn't ripe yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.90,0:10:52.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Looks like that time finally came.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.86,0:10:55.40,Main,,0,0,0,,No... not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.40,0:10:57.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.41,0:10:58.78,Main,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.78,0:11:00.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.66,0:11:04.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko isn't done yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.00,0:11:06.29,Main,,0,0,0,,My Kominato Ruko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.29,0:11:07.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Black Desire!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.42,0:11:12.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.97,0:11:19.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.64,0:11:26.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.86,0:11:37.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.15,0:11:38.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.24,0:11:40.12,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not Ru...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.12,0:11:40.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.95,0:11:44.08,Main,,0,0,0,,The voice, it's not Ru.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.08,0:11:47.96,Main,,0,0,0,,But, Tama probably knows
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.96,0:11:51.50,Main,,0,0,0,,that voice more than Ru's.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.38,0:11:55.59,Main,,0,0,0,,We finally meet, Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.59,0:11:57.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Who... Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.11,0:12:13.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Poor thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.11,0:12:15.40,Main,,0,0,0,,You're so bruised...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.70,0:12:20.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru is so mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.62,0:12:25.41,Main,,0,0,0,,It was a wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.41,0:12:28.87,Main,,0,0,0,,to be together, forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.87,0:12:31.96,Main,,0,0,0,,A wish you earnestly asked for...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.59,0:12:38.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru must care for her friends more than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.42,0:12:40.30,Main,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.30,0:12:42.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.30,0:12:45.39,Main,,0,0,0,,She said that she'll be friends with Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.39,0:12:46.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.27,0:12:49.60,Main,,0,0,0,,We're going to eat ice cream together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.60,0:12:53.48,Main,,0,0,0,,She said she'll buy me matching scrunchies!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.48,0:12:55.40,Main,,0,0,0,,--And...!\N--Poor, poor thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.53,0:13:00.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru is going through this for her friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.32,0:13:04.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Not for you, Tama,\Nbut for her precious friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.03,0:13:06.16,Main,,0,0,0,,to the extent she's trying to be an LRIG.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.16,0:13:07.58,Main,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.58,0:13:09.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru said we'll all go home together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.96,0:13:11.29,Main,,0,0,0,,That's why Tama has to--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.29,0:13:13.13,Main,,0,0,0,,That's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.13,0:13:16.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Everything is wrong, Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.09,0:13:17.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Remember...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.73,0:13:30.43,Main,,0,0,0,,It's easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.27,0:13:35.94,Main,,0,0,0,,You don't want to fulfill Ru's wish, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.94,0:13:37.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Then it's easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.98,0:13:40.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Just don't agree at the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.28,0:13:43.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki said it herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.32,0:13:48.62,Main,,0,0,0,,To fulfill the wish of a Selector,\Nthe LRIG needs to agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.58,0:13:53.17,Main,,0,0,0,,B-But then, Ru...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.17,0:13:56.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Then try and win.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.09,0:13:58.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Win the battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.05,0:14:01.17,Main,,0,0,0,,and then you'll know Ru's true feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.17,0:14:02.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.93,0:14:04.93,Main,,0,0,0,,That is, if you win the battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.51,0:14:08.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.01,0:14:09.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.73,0:14:12.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama? Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.94,0:14:16.36,Main,,0,0,0,,"Win... and you'll know..."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.36,0:14:18.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama, don't overdo yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.27,0:14:21.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru... Tama will battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.44,0:14:24.36,Main,,0,0,0,,This will be the last battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.36,0:14:25.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.33,0:14:29.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, that's a good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.24,0:14:32.54,Main,,0,0,0,,The battle isn't over yet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.54,0:14:33.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.91,0:14:36.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Ener Charge. Tama, level 4!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.92,0:14:40.38,Main,,0,0,0,,No matter what's beyond my wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.38,0:14:42.09,Main,,0,0,0,,...this is the last battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.09,0:14:45.26,Main,,0,0,0,,No matter what waits beyond my wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.26,0:14:47.43,Main,,0,0,0,,...this is the last battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.43,0:14:48.89,Main,,0,0,0,,--The last...!\N--The last...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.43,0:14:53.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.77,0:14:56.15,Main,,0,0,0,,The white and black\Nare colliding with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.90,0:14:59.61,Main,,0,0,0,,The battlefield...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.00,0:15:18.84,Main,,0,0,0,,The roof...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.84,0:15:22.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Were we returned from the battlefield?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.84,0:15:26.18,Main,,0,0,0,,No! The sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.18,0:15:28.51,Main,,0,0,0,,...and the others are still...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.77,0:15:39.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru! What should Tama do next?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.77,0:15:41.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.19,0:15:45.07,Main,,0,0,0,,It's so pretty...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.78,0:15:50.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I wasn't able to tell a little while ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.33,0:15:54.25,Main,,0,0,0,,but Ru and Grandma's house is around there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.25,0:15:56.33,Main,,0,0,0,,R-Ru...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.33,0:15:57.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.37,0:15:58.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.58,0:16:02.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama, you're showing me this\Nbefore we end, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.84,0:16:04.55,Main,,0,0,0,,End?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.47,0:16:07.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Grandma...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.59,0:16:11.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Goodbye...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.60,0:16:18.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Look, Iona. She already\Nthinks she's going to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.31,0:16:20.81,Main,,0,0,0,,She's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.81,0:16:23.19,Main,,0,0,0,,really the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.02,0:16:25.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.82,0:16:28.07,Main,,0,0,0,,What should I do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.03,0:16:35.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Before the final attack, an oath.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.04,0:16:37.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.08,0:16:43.75,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right... I took an\Noath with Hanayo-{\i1}san {\i0}too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.75,0:16:47.26,Main,,0,0,0,,That's supposed to be\Nthe final contract with the LRIG.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.26,0:16:51.09,Main,,0,0,0,,But... didn't Tama lose her memory?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.60,0:17:03.48,Main,,0,0,0,,What should I say, Tama?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.94,0:17:08.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru's not thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.99,0:17:13.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Not thinking of being able to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.54,0:17:20.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru is planning to become\Nan LRIG for her friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.58,0:17:24.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru is thinking of becoming an LRIG...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.50,0:17:27.05,Main,,0,0,0,,to save everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.01,0:17:29.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.92,0:17:33.76,Main,,0,0,0,,So, what do I have to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.76,0:17:36.43,Main,,0,0,0,,I... accept...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.43,0:17:38.27,Main,,0,0,0,,I accept...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.27,0:17:41.69,Main,,0,0,0,,...the laws... of the Selector...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.69,0:17:44.02,Main,,0,0,0,,...the laws of the Selector.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.33,0:17:59.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.41,0:18:05.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Awww, this is taking too long\Ndespite them not having moves left.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.50,0:18:07.88,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm bored already.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.88,0:18:11.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Go and let them have a really nice one!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.43,0:18:15.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Bloody Slash.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.10,0:18:18.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.93,0:18:20.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.10,0:18:21.77,Main,,0,0,0,,--White Hope!\N--White Hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.65,0:18:35.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-What? What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.03,0:18:37.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Say? What's going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.08,0:18:42.16,Main,,0,0,0,,It's... finally happening...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.30,0:18:55.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.09,0:18:57.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.56,0:19:02.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.02,0:19:08.65,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't regret this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.65,0:19:12.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Because no matter what happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.07,0:19:15.11,Main,,0,0,0,,this is what I chose for my wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.11,0:19:17.37,Main,,0,0,0,,What I chose...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.37,0:19:18.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.50,0:19:35.09,Main,,0,0,0,,No... Ruko won, so why...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.09,0:19:36.68,Main,,0,0,0,,The oath wasn't complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.68,0:19:38.01,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.01,0:19:40.10,Main,,0,0,0,,The last part of the oath.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.10,0:19:44.35,Main,,0,0,0,,The part, "Now, a new\NEternal Girl will be born."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.39,0:19:47.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.02,0:19:48.27,Main,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.27,0:19:51.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama can't make Ruko into an LRIG...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.48,0:19:54.82,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't want to say bye to Ruko...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.82,0:19:57.40,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.40,0:19:58.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.95,0:20:01.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.75,0:20:06.66,Main,,0,0,0,,It's going away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.66,0:20:08.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama! Please! The oath!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.79,0:20:11.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Please, again! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.59,0:20:14.88,Main,,0,0,0,,No... Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.31,0:20:24.68,Main,,0,0,0,,It can't be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.85,0:20:29.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-Why is Iona-{\i1}san{\i0}...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.61,0:20:35.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona was ready to have\Nher wish granted all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.98,0:20:39.99,Main,,0,0,0,,She won more than enough\Nin the Selector battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.99,0:20:45.79,Main,,0,0,0,,But, she lacked a certain condition\Nto have her wish come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.79,0:20:46.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.95,0:20:50.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Right. That's why her wish was on hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.42,0:20:53.34,Main,,0,0,0,,But, I guess your condition is met now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.34,0:20:55.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.59,0:20:58.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Now my wish will come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.76,0:21:00.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.97,0:21:10.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama! Please, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.02,0:21:12.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Hurry and make my wish come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.98,0:21:14.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.27,0:21:16.65,Main,,0,0,0,,--I accept...\N--I accept...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.65,0:21:19.07,Main,,0,0,0,,--...the laws of the Selector...\N--...the laws of the Selector...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.61,0:21:22.45,Main,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.45,0:21:24.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't... Please don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.78,0:21:27.62,Main,,0,0,0,,I need to return everyone...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.62,0:21:30.91,Main,,0,0,0,,--Now, a new Eternal Girl...\N--Now, a new Eternal Girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.91,0:21:32.67,Main,,0,0,0,,--...will be born!\N--...will be born!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.67,0:21:34.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.36,0:22:03.74,Main,,0,0,0,,I-Iona-{\i1}san{\i0}...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.50,0:22:12.37,Main,,0,0,0,,U-Urith...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.37,0:22:14.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's meet again,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.71,0:22:16.67,Main,,0,0,0,,scum.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.92,0:22:23.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.22,0:22:24.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.18,0:22:25.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Why...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.26,0:22:29.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Ta... ma...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.11,0:22:37.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Isn't this great,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.07,0:22:38.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.24,0:22:46.28,Main,,0,0,0,,This tastes great!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.28,0:22:49.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Grandma, your white sauce is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.79,0:22:55.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru-{\i1}chan {\i0}is quite late.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.42,0:22:57.71,Main,,0,0,0,,You should just eat already.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.71,0:22:59.59,Main,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.59,0:23:01.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Grandma...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.46,0:23:04.22,Main,,0,0,0,,wants to be with Ru-{\i1}chan{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.26,0:23:08.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.43,0:23:11.89,Main,,0,0,0,,wants to be with Ru.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.89,0:23:15.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...? Where are you, Tama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.48,0:23:17.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.90,0:23:21.53,Main,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.53,0:23:23.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama's wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.41,0:23:31.74,Main,,0,0,0,,It's been quite a while... scum.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.74,0:23:34.83,Main,,0,0,0,,So, who will be battling us first?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.83,0:23:36.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama was a bad girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.58,0:23:39.13,Main,,0,0,0,,You're my precious friend...!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.92,0:23:45.84,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Selector spread WIXOSS{\i0}.
